messages.text: Do u really think i believe n him?
Ur a senior n high school, come on..
last year i heard a thump on the roof then jingles downstairs on christmas eve..
Jus hadnt got my parents to fess up yet..
believe wat u want. i kno..
U have been placed on the ‘naughty list’
R u kidding?!?! hahaha, its absolutely comical!!
i heard my friend got put on it last year..
well, u r not exactly a saint..
So what?? I smoke a lil weed here, steal a couple stuff there, wats the big deal?
And there’s no return address.. So i cant even see who did it..
idk… like a loud bang outside..
i am.. ur the one who txted me..
language, that’s how u ended up on the naughty list..
did u leave cookies… not sure if it would help but u never kno…
Ive gotta see who it is..
he wont let u see him..
they say comet is always the irritated one..
The fireplace statue is turned over..
Lights on the tree are off..
i jus hope its not wat happened 2 my friend..
It’s a..a piece of hard rock..
It’s heavy.. and full of rocks 2..
No, this cant be true.. This cant be happening..
i feel 4 u, i rly do..
I didnt mean for the year 2 turn out like this..
u will have another year 2 atone 4 it.
yep. think u will see some change n behavior.
